{
  "stem": "1550.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then eventually, one fine day, a telegram arrived from the Jewish agency that volunteers from the camp are allowed to join the Jewish brigade group.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a great honor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because, for instance, Jews from England were not allowed, or from America, or from-- from anywhere else were not allowed to join them the Jewish Brigade Group, only from Palestine and from our camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, by the way, in the meantime, since we had a number of Czech citizens and Polish citizens, they were allowed-- about 80 Czech citizens were allowed to join the Czech Army.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And about 40 or 50 Polish citizens were allowed to join the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they left Mauritius in-- in several groups.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But since-- since, for instance, I was an Austrian citizen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like an enemy, alien, I wasn't allowed to-- to join the British Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Except, a few left also to join the British Pioneer Corps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were about 20 or 30 who joined the British Pioneer Corps, Austrians, Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everyone was Jewish in the camp practically.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I didn't want to join the-- the Pioneer Corps as an Austrian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when-- when this thing came in at the end of 1944, I volunteered together with about 40 or 50 other people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually, I signed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I found the thing here, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found the document here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I signed, officially, the declaration on February the 1, 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, it was already [LAUGHS] very late in the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I left shortly thereafter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, the rest of the-- my parents, stayed in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I left together with these other 40 people on a military transport, Mauritius for East Africa.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went from there to Kenya.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
